description:
Back in 1982, the same year that The Young Ones was conceived, Rik &quot;Drop Dead Fred&quot; Mayall also filmed this one-off special about a lovable loser called Kevin Turvey who considers himself to be a hard-hitting investigative reporter. Unfortunately his investigations never really go anywhere due to his uncanny knack for going off on random tangents. The Man Behind The Green Door also boasts appearances by Rik's buddies Robbie &quot;Rubeus Hagrid&quot; Coltrane and Adrian &quot;Eddie Hitler&quot; Edmondson.

ALSO AVAILABLE: Rik Mayall's Kevin Turvey Investigates (1981)

